WEBVTT

00:00:13.240 --> 00:00:13.960
Boss Chen.

00:00:14.400 --> 00:00:16.239
We're an asset management company.

00:00:16.719 --> 00:00:18.920
We just took over your debt portfolio from the bank.

00:00:20.199 --> 00:00:21.120
We came today

00:00:21.440 --> 00:00:23.280
to discuss the plan we're offering you.

00:00:24.760 --> 00:00:27.239
If you want to collect, get in line.

00:00:29.000 --> 00:00:30.320
We're not here to collect debt.

00:00:31.719 --> 00:00:33.159
We're here to help you pay it off.

00:00:34.640 --> 00:00:36.159
Your sales pitch has really evolved.

00:00:36.479 --> 00:00:38.679
Before, it was all about reducing interest

00:00:38.719 --> 00:00:40.320
and restructuring debt.

00:00:40.479 --> 00:00:42.280
Now you're giving me money instead?

00:00:42.719 --> 00:00:44.560
Do you even believe yourselves?

00:00:45.159 --> 00:00:46.640
I've got no blood left for you to suck.

00:00:46.719 --> 00:00:47.840
Just go on home.

00:00:51.439 --> 00:00:52.320
Show him.

00:00:55.079 --> 00:00:56.359
A duo, huh?

00:00:56.640 --> 00:00:57.759
You really value me.

00:01:00.920 --> 00:01:01.799
Boss Chen.

00:01:02.640 --> 00:01:03.439
I know.

00:01:03.840 --> 00:01:05.680
You don't want to be a deadbeat.

00:01:06.799 --> 00:01:08.200
Nobody wants nonstop phone calls

00:01:08.239 --> 00:01:09.439
or people blocking your door every day.

00:01:10.560 --> 00:01:11.560
The fish farm went bankrupt

00:01:11.560 --> 00:01:12.599
because of circumstances.

00:01:13.200 --> 00:01:14.200
It wasn't your choice.

00:01:15.560 --> 00:01:17.400
Everyone wants to live with dignity.

00:01:19.400 --> 00:01:20.400
And now,

00:01:20.760 --> 00:01:21.840
the chance is right in front of you.

00:01:23.120 --> 00:01:24.480
I'll pay off your debt for you.

00:01:25.280 --> 00:01:27.120
Once you're off the blacklist,

00:01:27.799 --> 00:01:29.319
you transfer your fish farm to me.

00:01:29.760 --> 00:01:30.560
How about it?

00:01:31.959 --> 00:01:34.640
But that lousy farm's been abandoned for years.

00:01:34.840 --> 00:01:36.560
If you want to take it over,

00:01:36.719 --> 00:01:38.319
you've got to put in the work,

00:01:38.400 --> 00:01:39.599
channel water, stock fingerlings.

00:01:40.000 --> 00:01:41.239
You won't figure it out.

00:01:41.319 --> 00:01:42.359
How long will it take you

00:01:42.359 --> 00:01:43.560
to get to this point?

00:01:44.599 --> 00:01:45.640
That's six million right there.

00:02:12.960 --> 00:02:13.680
I've paid it off.

00:02:13.719 --> 00:02:14.879
I've paid it all off.

00:02:15.800 --> 00:02:17.000
Congratulations, Boss Chen.

00:02:18.439 --> 00:02:19.439
Check his credit record.

00:02:19.680 --> 00:02:20.360
Okay, okay.

00:02:24.520 --> 00:02:25.840
No bad credit history.

00:02:27.080 --> 00:02:28.560
No record of default.

00:02:30.960 --> 00:02:31.560
Is that so?

00:02:31.800 --> 00:02:32.560
Wait here for me.

00:02:32.639 --> 00:02:33.800
I'll go print out

00:02:33.800 --> 00:02:34.759
the fish farm transfer agreement.

00:02:35.280 --> 00:02:35.840
Sure.

00:02:44.159 --> 00:02:44.759
Boss.

00:02:45.159 --> 00:02:46.439
Do you need to use the restroom?

00:02:47.080 --> 00:02:47.800
I'm good.

00:02:48.240 --> 00:02:49.319
You don't need to?

00:02:49.680 --> 00:02:50.439
Then I'll go.

00:03:02.039 --> 00:03:03.039
The rat ran off.

00:03:03.560 --> 00:03:04.680
Not fast enough, though.

00:03:06.560 --> 00:03:07.159
Xiao.

00:03:07.599 --> 00:03:09.000
So what's our next move?

00:03:09.639 --> 00:03:10.599
Get a few of the guys

00:03:10.960 --> 00:03:11.919
to scare him a bit.

00:03:13.080 --> 00:03:14.400
In case the cops trace it to us,

00:03:14.520 --> 00:03:15.560
we'll make him run far away.

00:03:15.719 --> 00:03:17.240
As long as they can't catch him for a while.

00:03:19.840 --> 00:03:21.159
Xiao, you really think of everything.

00:03:22.400 --> 00:03:24.879
But that guy's fish farm,

00:03:25.080 --> 00:03:25.879
are we just letting it go?

00:03:26.159 --> 00:03:26.879
The fish farm?

00:03:28.000 --> 00:03:29.000
Once the heat dies down,

00:03:29.120 --> 00:03:30.199
the fish farm will still be ours.

00:03:30.639 --> 00:03:31.840
Who cares about his fingerprint?

00:03:34.199 --> 00:03:34.800
Right.

00:03:37.120 --> 00:03:38.439
Luo Xiao has already wrapped up

00:03:38.439 --> 00:03:39.439
Brother Mao's debt portfolio.

00:03:39.800 --> 00:03:42.319
Funds were deposited directly through the underground bank.

00:03:42.759 --> 00:03:45.439
Six million landed in Fengmao's corporate account.

00:03:46.199 --> 00:03:48.680
All legal, fully processed.

00:03:59.400 --> 00:04:00.639
The carp's in the water.

00:04:01.719 --> 00:04:03.039
Quite the operator.

00:04:11.159 --> 00:04:11.680
Sis.

00:04:12.080 --> 00:04:13.479
Fengmao Company just received

00:04:13.479 --> 00:04:14.680
a payment of six million.

00:04:14.840 --> 00:04:17.519
Paid from the county rural bank's settlement account.

00:04:17.759 --> 00:04:20.040
Memo says it's debt settlement proceeds,

00:04:20.160 --> 00:04:21.000
collected and paid on behalf.

00:04:26.519 --> 00:04:27.079
Zhao Lin.

00:04:27.279 --> 00:04:28.160
I was just looking for you.

00:04:28.680 --> 00:04:30.639
Fengmao just got six million in.

00:04:30.759 --> 00:04:32.720
Payer is the county rural bank's settlement account.

00:04:32.959 --> 00:04:34.519
Listed as debt settlement proceeds,

00:04:34.600 --> 00:04:35.480
collected and paid on behalf.

00:04:36.360 --> 00:04:37.480
How did this come about?

00:04:38.199 --> 00:04:39.879
Last week, Fengmao spent 600,000

00:04:39.959 --> 00:04:41.759
to buy a bad debt package from the bank.

00:04:41.959 --> 00:04:43.519
Total book value: six million.

00:04:43.879 --> 00:04:44.839
It was supposed to be a dead loss,

00:04:44.959 --> 00:04:46.439
but somehow they collected on it.

00:04:46.920 --> 00:04:47.839
The debtor, Chen Guang,

00:04:47.920 --> 00:04:49.319
paid back all six million in full,

00:04:49.519 --> 00:04:50.399
collected by the bank,

00:04:50.600 --> 00:04:52.480
wired straight into Fengmao's corporate account.

00:04:53.319 --> 00:04:54.279
And Chen Guang's phone

00:04:54.279 --> 00:04:55.560
has been unreachable since last night.

00:04:55.720 --> 00:04:56.879
No one at his usual address either.

00:04:57.360 --> 00:04:58.959
I'll have command issue an APB right away.

00:04:59.040 --> 00:05:00.480
Check his vehicle and his address.

00:05:00.759 --> 00:05:01.079
Got it.

00:05:01.079 --> 00:05:01.639
Wait for me a sec.

00:05:01.639 --> 00:05:02.279
I've got something to give you.

00:05:02.439 --> 00:05:02.920
Okay.

00:05:18.879 --> 00:05:20.480
That's incredible.

00:05:21.040 --> 00:05:22.480
So that's how they launder money.

00:05:25.680 --> 00:05:26.439
Datou.

00:05:29.560 --> 00:05:31.240
I might need you to handle something for me.

00:05:32.600 --> 00:05:33.399
Just name it, bro.

00:05:40.319 --> 00:05:41.160
Attorney Xu.

00:05:41.600 --> 00:05:42.839
What big client is this,

00:05:43.040 --> 00:05:44.519
that needs you to greet him personally?

00:05:45.399 --> 00:05:46.839
Didn't they just set up

00:05:46.839 --> 00:05:48.600
a new asset management firm recently?

00:05:48.759 --> 00:05:50.399
They took a debt package from the bank,

00:05:50.600 --> 00:05:52.040
flipped it, and sold it for this much.

00:05:53.079 --> 00:05:53.800
Sixty?

00:05:53.879 --> 00:05:54.759
Six hundred.

00:05:56.839 --> 00:05:58.600
If we land this big client,

00:05:58.759 --> 00:06:00.160
won't you get a raise next year?

00:06:01.639 --> 00:06:02.639
Mr. Shi, Mr. Shi.

00:06:02.920 --> 00:06:03.800
Thanks for coming.

00:06:03.959 --> 00:06:04.759
The meeting room's right ahead.

00:06:04.920 --> 00:06:06.000
Thanks, thanks.

00:06:06.480 --> 00:06:07.720
Bring tea, the best one.

00:06:09.160 --> 00:06:11.399
Mr. Shi, you really are a distinguished guest.

00:06:12.360 --> 00:06:13.079
Here's the thing.

00:06:13.519 --> 00:06:15.319
Based on your company's business profile,

00:06:15.480 --> 00:06:16.240
asset acquisition,

00:06:16.319 --> 00:06:17.240
corporate debt management,

00:06:17.319 --> 00:06:18.319
project investment.

00:06:18.480 --> 00:06:19.560
Personally, I believe

00:06:20.000 --> 00:06:20.759
this gentleman,

00:06:21.360 --> 00:06:23.160
Attorney Chen Ming,

00:06:23.399 --> 00:06:24.399
is a perfect fit for you.

00:06:24.519 --> 00:06:25.720
He's handled many corporate mergers

00:06:25.720 --> 00:06:26.920
and debt settlement cases.

00:06:27.079 --> 00:06:28.279
Especially with our company's

00:06:28.279 --> 00:06:30.160
private asset operation procedures,

00:06:30.240 --> 00:06:31.360
he is highly familiar.

00:06:36.720 --> 00:06:37.879
And please take a look at this one,

00:06:38.240 --> 00:06:39.959
Attorney Li Jing.

00:06:40.120 --> 00:06:41.920
She specializes in helping high-net-worth clients

00:06:42.040 --> 00:06:43.480
manage investments and finances.

00:06:43.759 --> 00:06:44.519
If down the road,

00:06:44.600 --> 00:06:45.800
your company has any business

00:06:45.800 --> 00:06:47.319
needs in this area,

00:06:47.399 --> 00:06:48.759
I'm sure Attorney Li

00:06:48.839 --> 00:06:51.680
can definitely help you control the risks.

00:06:52.480 --> 00:06:54.399
I want Attorney Luo Xiao to continue.

00:06:55.720 --> 00:06:56.560
Luo...

00:06:59.680 --> 00:07:02.319
Mr. Shi, Luo Xiao,

00:07:02.600 --> 00:07:03.839
he's no longer with the firm.

00:07:13.720 --> 00:07:15.240
Then bring him back.

00:07:17.879 --> 00:07:19.160
Here's the thing, Mr. Shi.

00:07:19.560 --> 00:07:21.519
Besides these two, our firm has

00:07:21.519 --> 00:07:23.879
many other excellent attorneys.

00:07:23.959 --> 00:07:24.720
I'm confident that going forward,

00:07:24.720 --> 00:07:26.199
through our partnership,

00:07:26.279 --> 00:07:28.199
these attorneys' capabilities

00:07:28.279 --> 00:07:30.399
will be more reliable than Luo Xiao's.

00:07:31.240 --> 00:07:32.160
You know what,

00:07:32.279 --> 00:07:34.000
Fengmao and your firm

00:07:34.079 --> 00:07:35.160
really do have quite a connection.

00:07:35.600 --> 00:07:37.160
Those companies you've worked with lately,

00:07:37.160 --> 00:07:38.160
what were they called again?

00:07:39.560 --> 00:07:40.759
Tianhui Group,

00:07:41.839 --> 00:07:42.839
Xingchen Holdings,

00:07:43.240 --> 00:07:45.720
and Mingcheng Real Estate, right?

00:07:46.240 --> 00:07:48.319
What a coincidence, we're investing in them too.

00:07:51.240 --> 00:07:51.920
Alright then.

00:07:52.360 --> 00:07:54.439
The client's needs always come first.

00:07:54.560 --> 00:07:55.879
One moment, let me make a call.

00:07:56.000 --> 00:07:56.839
No need.

00:07:59.439 --> 00:08:00.199
Xiao.

00:08:06.120 --> 00:08:08.240
Attorney Xu, long time no see.

00:08:27.600 --> 00:08:28.279
Please, go ahead.

00:08:28.560 --> 00:08:29.240
Attorney Xu.

00:08:35.679 --> 00:08:36.559
Detective Zhang.

00:08:37.639 --> 00:08:39.519
I get that you want to catch them red-handed,

00:08:39.799 --> 00:08:41.600
but money laundering isn't a street brawl.

00:08:41.799 --> 00:08:43.519
There's no knife, no bloodstains left behind.

00:08:44.120 --> 00:08:44.919
What we can offer

00:08:44.919 --> 00:08:46.559
is the money trail and the logic chain.

00:08:47.399 --> 00:08:49.679
While investigating the homicide,

00:08:49.879 --> 00:08:51.559
we already picked up on these things.

00:08:52.799 --> 00:08:55.000
Between Fengmao Company and Shengquan,

00:08:55.000 --> 00:08:58.320
there are indeed some abnormal fund flows.

00:08:58.840 --> 00:09:00.559
But Fengmao's books have one oddity:

00:09:00.720 --> 00:09:02.039
the cash ratio is way too high.

00:09:02.519 --> 00:09:04.080
Meaning, unlike other companies,

00:09:04.080 --> 00:09:05.120
they don't rely on paper transactions.

00:09:05.240 --> 00:09:06.679
They swallow cash directly.

00:09:07.000 --> 00:09:08.679
And if they're swallowing it, they need somewhere to stash it.

00:09:08.919 --> 00:09:10.159
We suspect

00:09:11.240 --> 00:09:13.360
Fengmao Company very likely

00:09:13.440 --> 00:09:14.879
has set up a fixed location

00:09:14.960 --> 00:09:17.399
to centrally store the dirty cash.

00:09:17.799 --> 00:09:18.679
Suspect?

00:09:19.200 --> 00:09:19.759
No, no.

00:09:19.759 --> 00:09:21.399
It's this Chen Yongjiang case.

00:09:22.000 --> 00:09:23.919
The situation keeps shifting,

00:09:24.000 --> 00:09:25.440
and it involves a lot of parties.

00:09:25.720 --> 00:09:27.440
So if we rely on manual screening,

00:09:27.440 --> 00:09:28.559
the scope is just too wide.

00:09:28.720 --> 00:09:29.679
We were thinking maybe you

00:09:29.679 --> 00:09:32.080
could narrow down some key targets for us,

00:09:32.559 --> 00:09:34.000
so we can focus our investigation.

00:09:34.279 --> 00:09:35.240
I've been thinking about

00:09:35.279 --> 00:09:36.879
where Fengmao stashes all that cash,

00:09:37.120 --> 00:09:39.720
somewhere safe and easy to move.

00:09:40.480 --> 00:09:41.240
How about this:

00:09:41.559 --> 00:09:43.480
I'll mark the key dates in the books

00:09:43.480 --> 00:09:45.360
and the funding peaks for you,

00:09:45.559 --> 00:09:47.039
to help with your stakeouts and surveillance.

00:10:15.080 --> 00:10:15.759
Boss.

00:10:15.960 --> 00:10:17.080
So in that case,

00:10:17.279 --> 00:10:19.480
are we still renting Brother Mao's warehouse?

00:10:29.279 --> 00:10:30.679
That plot of land next door,

00:10:31.639 --> 00:10:32.600
how much does it go for?

00:11:45.559 --> 00:11:46.240
Brother-in-law!

00:11:49.960 --> 00:11:50.759
Brother-in-law!

00:11:51.440 --> 00:11:52.159
Brother-in-law!

00:11:53.120 --> 00:11:54.000
You're back.

00:11:56.600 --> 00:11:57.600
What are you doing here?

00:11:58.320 --> 00:12:01.000
Well, isn't it Huang Qiuping's funeral?

00:12:01.399 --> 00:12:02.320
She died at that auto repair shop.

00:12:02.320 --> 00:12:03.759
I gotta go give some condolence money.

00:12:07.240 --> 00:12:07.759
Boss.

00:12:07.879 --> 00:12:08.440
Come on.

00:12:08.799 --> 00:12:09.600
Step out for a sec.

00:12:12.399 --> 00:12:13.840
Isn't he the...

00:12:14.320 --> 00:12:14.960
Boss.

00:12:15.200 --> 00:12:16.559
Let me introduce you. This is my brother-in-law,

00:12:17.519 --> 00:12:18.519
Shi Qijun.

00:12:18.919 --> 00:12:19.600
Officer Zhang.

00:12:19.840 --> 00:12:22.039
I locked him up once before.

00:12:22.360 --> 00:12:23.600
How long ago was that?

00:12:23.759 --> 00:12:24.840
Seven or eight years, I'd say.

00:12:25.279 --> 00:12:26.000
A fight back in the village.

00:12:26.039 --> 00:12:27.679
They called him in just to make up the numbers.

00:12:27.759 --> 00:12:29.039
Ended up with three guys getting beat up.

00:12:29.240 --> 00:12:31.440
And then you took the fall for someone.

00:12:32.960 --> 00:12:34.159
Loyalty's a good thing,

00:12:34.600 --> 00:12:36.320
but if you follow the wrong people,

00:12:36.600 --> 00:12:37.559
if you can't read them right,

00:12:38.240 --> 00:12:39.600
it's easy to drag yourself down with them.

00:12:41.279 --> 00:12:42.679
Back then I was young.

00:12:43.159 --> 00:12:43.879
I mean, you come over,

00:12:43.879 --> 00:12:45.080
and you don't even give us a heads-up.

00:12:45.080 --> 00:12:46.639
Your sister hasn't prepared a thing.

00:12:47.000 --> 00:12:48.399
My sis sent you a message, didn't she?

00:12:48.480 --> 00:12:49.600
Didn't you check your phone?

00:12:53.559 --> 00:12:55.080
Pretty busy, huh, brother-in-law?

00:12:56.200 --> 00:12:57.559
All right, all right.

00:12:57.639 --> 00:12:59.600
Boss, go take care of your work.

00:12:59.679 --> 00:13:00.559
Take my car.

00:13:00.799 --> 00:13:01.480
Got it. Let's go.

00:13:01.600 --> 00:13:02.440
Come sit inside. Let's go.

00:13:02.559 --> 00:13:03.240
No, no, no.

00:13:03.919 --> 00:13:05.519
I've already bought the groceries.

00:13:05.639 --> 00:13:07.840
Tonight the three of us are having a real bro's feast.

00:13:09.000 --> 00:13:10.159
Don't bother.

00:13:10.519 --> 00:13:12.799
Haven't seen him in years, right?

00:13:12.799 --> 00:13:13.840
Let's chat for a bit, come on.

00:13:14.759 --> 00:13:17.000
Hey, your hair's gotten shorter too.

00:13:17.120 --> 00:13:17.919
Hasn't it?

00:13:19.159 --> 00:13:20.720
Why are you with him...

00:13:28.759 --> 00:13:31.000
Brother-in-law, you've got the keys.

00:13:33.879 --> 00:13:34.519
Come on, come on.

00:13:34.559 --> 00:13:35.399
Come on, this way.

00:13:36.120 --> 00:13:36.919
Let's go, let's go.